t the date and time (from available slots) which is suitable to the patient. Click on \"Book Appointment\" to complete booking an appointment with the specialist doctor. Config file is missing. Follow up on Failed to send OTP OTP is incorrect! OTP Verification Failed! Treat mild fever at home What is Anemia? Treat cough at home Benefits of walking out of Pending Exit App Last sync Help center Help Selected date Today Close patient registration? Are you sure you want to close the patient registration? Health Training About App Are you sure you want to change language to %1$s? Change language? Language successfully changed! Changing protocols Please wait while the protocols are being changed. Protocols have been successfully changed! Overall Daily Date Range Visit Date Patient Registered! Does the patient want to start the visit now? No address added No country added No state added No district added No city added No postal code added No phone number added Follow up scheduled! A follow up for this patient visit has been scheduled successfully. Downloaded to: The doctor suggested a follow-up visit on %1$s Downloaded Successfully Prescription is up to date. Select all the answers Some issue with the mindmaps. of questions %1$d/%2$d Visit reason Please select the range! Level %1$d Please drag to select! Select yes or no Select Duration Type Please select the date Please select at least one option! Failed to change password Speciality must not be null Please select time slot Booking Appointment! Results for Appointment! Today at has an appointment with %1$d/%2$d Physical Examination %1$d/%2$d. Medical history: Family history Add image by Please take \'s follow-up visit. Hello this is %1$s from Telemedicine project. I am connecting with you regarding your recent visit. Please wait for the doctor message! Doctor is yet to send the prescriptions for patients you can remind the doctor. Please select at least one complaint! are awaiting their prescriptions. cm kg kg/m bpm breat